Simon Tsui -- Systems Final Project

Idea
The goal of the project is to make a Tamagotchi pet for the user to care for

User Interface
Text will be displayed on the current info for the pet, its levels, contentedness

Implementation

Front-end: Terminal display of pet information via stdout
User input received via stdin

Saving Implementation
Progress can be saved by uploading it to the server, will be stored in different files (pipe, redirect)

Allocated memory
Different attributes of the pet will be stored in arrays

Signal handling
Bad user input will be accounted for so the game won't crash.

Multiplayer feature?
Interacting with one another's pets, two players simultaneously (networking)
